  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'It will take a while to analyze the data from your PurpleTooth
      transmitter, but if my suspicions are correct, things are not looking good.


      I''ve
      re-activated an old ATM for you to train with so you can hone your skills.'
    nextOption: What's an ATM?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: An Automated Tellemonster Machine.
    nextOption: That sounds dangerous
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Exactly the point!


      That body is a combat model, and we
      used to use the ATMs to verify they were in good shape.


      If the path
      ahead is as difficult as I think, you''ll need all the practice you can get...'
    nextOption: Gulp
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Head up to the top of the pyramid and you should see a new time
      crystal near the Body-Matic 2000.


      Take it to the Arena of trials and
      get started on your training.'
    nextOption: Ok, I'll be back... I hope...
  prerequisiteConditions: []
